title: Here’s to the Zeits I’ll never remember... 8/25: Apple Crisp Macchiato, Magic Key Pass, Aaliyah, NFL, OnlyFans, Krispy Kreme, New Zealand
itunes:title: Here’s to the Zeits I’ll never remember... 8/25: Apple Crisp Macchiato, Magic Key Pass, Aaliyah, NFL, OnlyFans, Krispy Kreme, New Zealand
description:
In this edition of Here’s to the Zeits I’ll never remember, Jack and Miles discuss the new Starbucks Apple Crisp Macchiato, Disneyland's 'Magic Key' Pass, the 20 year anniversary of Aaliyah's death, the NFL's QBs being pro-disease, OnlyFans flip-flopping like a fish, Krispy Kreme upping the ante, and New Zealand finally joining the rest of us in the Pandemic
